multithreading ideas?

TSTART cpu, sp, ip
TSTARTW cpu, sp, ip
TSTARTO cpu, sp, ip
CPUHALT
TJOIN cpu
TSTOP cpu
TMAIL cpu, reg
TMAILBOX reg, reg(err)
TMAILBOXW reg, reg(err)
TQUERY cpu
TPROCN reg
MOFF

TJOIN waits until cpu hits CPUHALT
then picks back up on calling thread

TSTOP stops a processor

CPUHALT halts thread and notifies TJOINs

MOFF powers off mobo

other ideas:
OUT port, leaf, reg
IN port, leaf, reg

OUTB port, leaf, reg
INB port, leaf, reg

LEAF 0: 
	MANUFACTURER 
LEAF 1:
	DEVICE NAME


